title: "Deduplicate history, restore, and redaction replay helpers"
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: jscpd found history/restore/redaction commands repeat history patch normalization and replay helpers. Representative clones include history.ts:118-139 vs restore.ts:91-112, history.ts:139-167 vs restore.ts:213-241, history-redact.ts:292-313 vs restore.ts:91-112, history-redact.ts:320-339 vs history.ts:139-232, history-redact.ts:455-465 vs history.ts:173-183, and history-redact.ts:502-516 vs restore.ts:334-348. Existing pm-xk39 tracks the redaction feature, but no active item covers extracting shared replay/patch mechanics across commands. Fix by moving common history-entry read, patch normalization, replay apply, and subject resolution helpers into a shared history command module used by history, restore, and history-redact."
